   <H1>Julie Kessler</H1>

</CENTER>

Julie Kessler, Director of Academic Programs.  
Miss Kessler is a candidate for the Ph.D. in 
Political Philosophy at The Claremont Graduate 
School and a graduate of Ashland University in 
Ashland, Ohio.

