Penn.<br>
<B>Oct. 26</B>-Addresses Cincinnati Crisis Pregnancy Center, Cincinnati,
Ohio.<br>
<B>Nov. 9</B>-Addresses Indiana Family Institute banquet, Evansville,
Ind.<br>
</ul><p>
<B>FRC On Air</B>
<p><ul>
