<title>June 1995 Washington Watch Newsletter</title>
<body>
<center><img src="/townhall/FRC/wwatch/wwatch.gif"></center>
<p>
Volume 6<br>
Number 8<br>
June 13, 1995
<p><hr width=60% size=3><p>
<center><h2>CONTENTS</h2></center>
<font size=+1>
<ul><ul><ul><a href="#blueprint">The Blueprint</a></font>
<ul type=ball><li><a href="#life">Restoring the Sanctity of Human Life</a>
<li><a href="#education">Empower Parents for Education</a>
<li><a href="#purse">Protect the Family Purse</a>
<li><a href="#wilderness">Tame the Cultural Wilderness</a>
