	Brother Rice High School, Bloomfield Hills, MI. May, 1994
		Graduated with highest honors after fulfilling college prepatory requirements and
		receiving Advanced Placement credit.
		Final Grade Point Average:  3.95
		Honors and Activities:      Model United Nations National
		Debate Champion ('91-'94)
			Optimists International Award
			Student Council
			Forensics/Debate

<h3>Experience</h3>
	Nancy Rosen and Company, Birmingham, MI Summer '95
