AND DEVELOPMENT IN CENTRAL AMERICA</B> </A></CENTER>
<P>
Monday, 29 July 1996<BR>
10.00-11.30 hours<BR>
United Nations University Headquarters, Tokyo<BR>

<P>
The Foreign Ministers from four Central American countries will
gather at the United Nations University Headquarters for a panel
discussion on Peace, Democracy and Development in Central America
at 10.00 hours on Monday, 29 July 1996.
