Minister on the experiences of his country in peace, democracy
and development within the Central American context. Following
individual presentations there will be a time for discussion and
question and answers involving the audience. The discussion will
be moderated by Prof. Heitor Gurgulino de Souza, Rector of the
United Nations University.
