<H2>Under Construction</H2>
<P>
<H3>Media Expeditions</H3>
<p>
<BLOCKQUOTE>EXPEDITION EARTH is organizing a media expedition where participants will utilize their unique skills in exploring and documenting a new environment, a different culture and a spectacular natural phonomenon.  Selected materials from the expedition will be digitized and presented on Expedition Earth's web site.  Help us create a digital database of our changing planet.  We invite your comments and suggestions.   <A HREF="mailto:wowla@earthlink.net">E-mail Expedition Earth.</A>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
