<hr size=5 width=20%>
<H3>Native American Relief effort</H3>
<P>
<BLOCKQUOTE>SKYBAND RESOURCES, an Expedition Earth affiliate, is a relief agency dedicated to the collection and distribution of urgently needed resources to Native American people.  Project director Francine Kokenis has successfully delivered truckloads of food and clothing to Indian reservations across the United States.  For further information on Skyband Resopurces, please call Ms. Kokenis at (310) 472-7300. </BLOCKQUOTE>

