<DD>All three youth principals are contributing writers to international environmental magazines Grassroots and Grassroots Youth Magazine(a publication for <i>Partners for the Planet</i>), published journalists and accomplished public speakers.<P>

<DD>Gail Church 
<DD>Executive Director TREE MUSKETEERS
<DD>Adult Administrator '95 National <i>Partners for the Planet</i> Youth Summit
<DD>Contributing writer/Editorial Liason Grassroots Youth Magazine<P>
</DL></DT>
