http://nko.org:80/millennium/gupdate.html 164.122.9.45 19970216011854 text/html 4414
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Sunday, 16-Feb-97 01:17:07 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 24-Apr-96 17:48:19 GMT
