<TITLE>Issue 15-2</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#96E1FA">

<P>
<B><FONT SIZE=5>Issue 15: Changing Work, Unemployment,
Leisure, and Underemployment<BR>
</FONT></B>
<P>
<B><FONT FACE="Times New Roman">For your information, related
items from Round 1, and rated in Round 2:</FONT></B><FONT FACE="Times New Roman">
This table presents the developments previously suggested by respondents,
the average of judgments about likelihood and importance, and
the most frequently suggested agencies that respondents felt should
be involved. UNO includes all UN organizations and functions such
as peacekeeping ,  International Atomic Energy Agency, UNDP, UNICEF,
UNEP, and affiliated agencies such as WHO, World Bank and IMF.
<BR>
</FONT>
<P>
